    </exercise>

    <exercise number="29"><statement><p>
        The figure shows a graph of <m>w(t) = -10(t+1)^3+10 </m>. Solve the following:</p><p>
        <sidebyside width="40%"><image source="images/fig-2-2-29"><description>cubic transformed</description></image></sidebyside>
        <ol label="a" cols="2">
            <li><p><m>-10(t+1)^3+10=100</m></p></li>
            <li><p><m>-10(t+1)^3+10=-140</m></p></li>
