    <exercise number="61"><statement><p><m>f(x)=\dfrac{1}{x} </m></p></statement>
    <answer><p><ol label="a">
        <li><p>Not always true: <m>f (1 + 2)\ne f (1) + f (2)</m> because <m>\frac{1}{3} \ne\frac{3}{2} </m>.</p></li>
        <li><p>True: <m>\frac{1}{ab} = \frac{1}{a}\cdot\frac{1}{b} </m></p></li>
    </ol></p></answer>
    </exercise>

